Interface PDTBAttribute

All Known Implementing Classes:
PDTBNodeImpl.PDTBAttributeImpl
public interface PDTBAttribute

An attribute asscoiated with a PDTBNode. Attributes are maintained in addition to features, as a convenience to provide XPath support.
